Cell["\<\
FindReflection[g, x, a] reflects x through a: returns vertices x' satisfying \
B(x, a, x') and d(a, x) == d(a, x'). Returns a List of unary InfraPoint[{x'}] \
wrappers; n / UpTo[n] / All control multiplicity.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"1e978ae5-df90-42c3-b27c-b40866fa10b2"],

